beer.beer_description:
An orange, lemon lime Berliner Weiss brewed exclusively for the 2024 Beer Cartel Advent Calendar.

We distilled local citrus on our rotary evaporator to layer orange, lemon & lime to this classic Berliner Weiss as gently as baubles on a fresh Christmas tree.
